           <head>PRIMUS CATALOGUS PERSONARUM ANNI <date when="1615">1615</date>
           [PROVINCIAE PHILIPPINARUM]</head>
           
           <p>Ex his qui ex <placeName key="Japonia">Japonia</placeName> venerunt
           
           <lb/>Remanent adhuc in hac Provincia
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Melchior de Mora S.J.">Melchior de Mora</persName> 
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Franciscus Calderón S.J.">Franciscus Calderón</persName> 
              <lb/>P. García Garcés 
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Suares, Bartholomeus S.J.">Bartholomeus Suárez</persName> 
              <lb/>H.°<persName key="Vota, Agustinus S.J.">Augustinus Vota</persName> 
              <lb/>H. <persName key="Figueredo, Thomas de">Thomas de Figueredo</persName>
              <lb/>H. Michael Matçuda              
              <lb/>H. <persName key="Petrus Chiquan S.J.">Petrus Chiquam</persName> 
              <lb/>H. Román
              <lb/>H. Georgius
              <lb/>H. Alexius
              <lb/>H. Thadeus
              <lb/> 
              <lb/>Reversi sunt in <placeName key="Japonia">Japoniam</placeName>
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Vieyra, Sebastianus S.J.">Sebastianus Vieyra</persName> 
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Martinus Moan S.J.">Martinus Moan</persName>
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Yuqui, Didacus S.J.">Didacus Yuqui</persName>
              <lb/>H. <persName key="Bartholomeus Reoxey S.J.">Bartholomeus Reoxey</persName>	
              <lb/>H. <persName key="Amacusa, Andrés S.J.">Andrés Amacusa</persName>
              <lb/> 
              <lb/>Vita functus
              <lb/>H. <persName key="Paulus Reoyn S.J.">Paulus Reoyn</persName>, <placeName key="Manila">Manilae</placeName> <date when="1615-09-17">17 Septembris anni 1615</date>.
              <lb/> 
              <lb/>P. <persName key="Morejón, Petrus S.J.">Petrus Morejón</persName>, Procurator <placeName key="Japonia">Japoniae</placeName> ad Urbem, navigavit in <placeName key="Hispania" ref="https://pleiades.stoa.org/places/1027">Hispaniam</placeName>.
              <lb/>. . . . .
              <lb/>Scriptum <placeName key="Manila">Manilae</placeName>. <date when="1616-08-12">12. die Augusti, an. 1616</date>.
              <lb/><persName key="Valerius de Ledesma S.J.">Valerius de Ledesma</persName></p>
           
